data.description: Impeccably maintained 2/2 residence with double garage, spacious bedrooms, and large eat-in kitchen. The master bedroom features a walk-in closet and French doors opening to a deck overlooking a beautifully landscaped yard with a Diamond Brite pool. The 2005-installed rolled tile roof outshines S-tile. Conveniently located in a well-maintained NE neighborhood near the beach and I-95. Recent upgrades include a new water line, enhanced landscape lighting, new A/C, water heater, fresh paint, crown molding, and impact windows/doors. Outdoor amenities include a remodeled garage, 4-stage sprinkler system, outdoor speakers, and a new privacy fence. This home combines style and functionality, offering a comfortable and visually appealing living space.
